Requirements specification
- The program will generate a random number for the user to guess 1-10.
- The program will tell the user how far off they are.

System Analysis
-The system will generate a random number using the random module.
-The user will input a guess.
-The system will generate 4 responses to give the user based on how close they are to the number generated.

System Design
-The system will use the random module.
-The system will use if statements to generate the response.

